 After I remove my makeup, I clean my face and I do that with the Clarasonic Mia 2 

00:00:35.460 --> 00:00:38.620
 This is the pink and also the mini version. 

00:00:38.620 --> 00:00:44.300
 It is actually an automatic brush that, when turned on, moves around against your skin. 

